ao, Lei and Mylnikova, Liudmila N. and Larsson, Lars and Metz, Laure and Yeppiskoposyan, Levon and Pedersen, Lisbeth and Sarti, Lucia and Orlando, Ludovic and Slimak, Ludovic and Klassen, Lutz and Blank, Malou and González-Morales, Manuel and Silvestrini, Mara and Vretemark, Maria and Nesterova, Marina S. and Rykun, Marina and Rolfo, Mario Federico and Szmyt, Marzena and Przybyła, Marcin and Calattini, Mauro and Sablin, Mikhail and Dobisíková, Miluše and Meldgaard, Morten and Johansen, Morten and Berezina, Natalia and Card, Nick and Saveliev, Nikolai A. and Poshekhonova, Olga and Rickards, Olga and Lozovskaya, Olga V. and Uldum, Otto Christian and Aurino, Paola and Kosintsev, Pavel and Courtaud, Patrice and Ríos, Patricia and Mortensen, Peder and Lotz, Per and Persson, Per Åke and Bangsgaard, Pernille and Damgaard, Peter de Barros and Petersen, Peter Vang and Martinez, Pilar Prieto and Włodarczak, Piotr and Smolyaninov, Roman V. and Maring, Rikke and Menduiña, Roberto and Badalyan, Ruben and Iversen, Rune and Turin, Ruslan and Vasilyiev, Sergey and Wåhlin, Sidsel and Borutskaya, Svetlana and Skochina, Svetlana and Sørensen, Søren Anker and Andersen, Søren H. and Jørgensen, Thomas and Serikov, Yuri B. and Molodin, Vyacheslav I. and Smrcka, Vaclav and Merz, Victor and Appadurai, Vivek and Moiseyev, Vyacheslav and Magnusson, Yvonne and Kjær, Kurt H. and Lynnerup, Niels and Lawson, Daniel J. and Sudmant, Peter H. and Rasmussen, Simon and Korneliussen, Thorfinn and Durbin, Richard and Nielsen, Rasmus and Delaneau, Olivier and Werge, Thomas and Racimo, Fernando and Kristiansen, Kristian and Willerslev, Eske}, 
journal = {bioRxiv}, 
